name: MoonJuice
description:
MoonJuice, the Blockchain Powered Energy Drink, bridging the gap between retail and crypto! We offer a unique set of use cases for our holders, including 'dividends' from product sales, staking for DAO participation, and access to exclusive events which we sponsor.

We plan to partner with many big names in the art & music industry, and collaborate with them on NFT based product releases.
